` + "`" + `interactive-steward` + "`" + ` / ` + "`" + `queue_steward` + "`" + `. Explicit worker commands
(` + "`" + `ddx work` + "`" + `, ` + "`" + `ddx try <id>` + "`" + `, "execute bead ` + "`" + `<id>` + "`" + `") route to
